{"title":"樱花咏","authors":["彭龄"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":4,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"樱花咏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彭龄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天坛月季园的樱花正含苞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一簇簇红骨朵迎人笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说年年岁岁花相似啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分明它今春格外娇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"樱花呀，樱花——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中日人民新佳话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是春风说与你知道？……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一簇簇红骨朵迎人笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知道！知道！早知道！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周总理赋诗咏岚山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一方诗碑快刻好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待那时，岚山下——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万株樱花拥诗碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象丹云拥着总理笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说那诗句石上刻？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不！句句都在心上描！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"樱花盼望周总理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨不能一夜尽放苞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈！盼哪，盼哪，盼到了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周总理生前许下愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天由邓大姐实现了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一簇簇红骨朵迎人笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天坛月季园的樱花正含苞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着樱花想东邻呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风送暖旭日高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听！一阵阵，春风里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔海又传多少新佳话？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一霎时，红樱齐变彩云飘！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}